e-0", "recommendationservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["checkoutservice-0", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "matched_anomaly": "Please analyze the abnormal event between 2025-06-11T10:10:44Z and 2025-06-11T10:31:44Z and provide the root cause.", "time_range": "2025-06-11 10:10:44+00:00 to 2025-06-11 10:31:44+00:00"}, "metric_data_collected": true, "node_pod_mapping": {"aiops-k8s-01": ["checkoutservice-1", "emailservice-1", "productcatalogservice-1", "recommendationservice-2", "shippingservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-02": [], "aiops-k8s-03": ["shippingservice-2", "frontend-0", "adservice-0", "recommendationservice-1", "paymentservice-1", "cartservice-0"], "aiops-k8s-04": ["checkoutservice-0", "frontend-2", "currencyservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-05": ["paymentservice-2", "currencyservice-0", "cartservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-06": ["emailservice-2", "productcatalogservice-0", "checkoutservice-2"], "aiops-k8s-07": ["shippingservice-1", "frontend-1", "emailservice-0", "currencyservice-2", "adservice-1"], "aiops-k8s-08": ["recommendationservice-0", "productcatalogservice-2", "paymentservice-0", "cartservice-2", "adservice-2", "redis-cart-0"]}, "log_analysis_findings": "Based on the analysis of the logs provided, here is the summary of the findings:\n\n### Detected Log Keywords\n- `AdService--stress`\n- `Exception in thread \"Attach Listener\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException`\n- `Agent failed to start!`\n- `attempting to load Byteman agent more than once`\n\n### Hypotheses\n1. **Component**: Adservice\n   - **Reason**: The logs consistently show the presence of \"AdService--stress\" along with repeated attempts to load the Byteman agent, leading to failures. The `InvocationTargetException` suggests an issue in running the stress helper, possibly related to an agent reloading problem.\n   - **Evidence**: Multiple logs contain phrases like `Agent failed to start!` and attempts to load the agent multiple times.\n\n### Conclusion\nIt appears that the `adservice` is experiencing repeated attempts to invoke stress tests using Byteman, which may be due to incorrect configuration leading to failed agent starts. This consistent pattern points towards a root cause related to configuration or resource management issues within the `adservice`.\n\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_log_keys\": [\n    \"AdService--stress\",\n    \"Exception in thread \\\"Attach Listener\\\" java.lang.reflect.InvocationTargetException\",\n    \"Agent failed to start!\",\n    \"attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Repeated attempts to execute stress tests via Byteman agent led to invocation errors and agent start failures.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Logs showing \\\"Agent failed to start!\\\" and \\\"attempting to load Byteman agent more than once\\\" indicate a possible misconfiguration or resource handling issue.\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\nThese insights should assist in further diagnosis and resolution of the issues facing the adservice component.", "trace_analysis_findings": "```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_trace_keys\": [\n    \"latency_spike\",\n    \"frontend->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\",\n    \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n    \"cartservice->redis\"\n  ],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"frontend->cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Significant latency spike detected in 'hipstershop.CartService/GetCart' operations\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Anomaly average duration: up to 25,876ms vs normal average: ~2,535ms (~10x increase in delay).\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice->redis\",\n      \"reason\": \"Redis HGET and HMSET operations show drastic latency increase.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"HGET: Anomaly average ~8,935ms vs normal ~1,739ms; HMSET: 22,533ms vs ~1,361ms (10-15x degradation).\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"checkoutservice->cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"Errors propagate upstream to checkout service, calling CartService heavily impacted.\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Observed 46,378ms spike in 'POST /hipstershop.CartService/GetCart' (normal ~2,556ms).\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```", "metric_analysis_findings": "根据提供的 Trace 数据分析结果，以下是初始扫描阶段的发现：\n\n### 异常指标提取\n从异常指标 CSV 中，选择绝对值变化 `change_ratio` 最大的 Top 3 指标：\n1. `rrt` (服务延迟): adservice，变动 1.4834\n2. `pod_cpu_usage` (Pod CPU 使用率): adservice-1, adservice-2, adservice-0, 变动 2.0\n3. `rrt_max` (服务最大延迟): cartservice, 变动 1.4718\n\n### 初步分析与假设\n1. **adservice-1, adservice-2, adservice-0 Pod 的 CPU 使用率显著增加**\n   - 这三个 Pod 的 CPU 使用率上升到 0.6 (原为 0.01)，变化率达到 1.9344 和 2.0。\n   - 虽然名字显示为 Pod，但由于它们位于同一个物理节点 aiops-k8s-08，可能与该节点资源瓶颈或其他底层问题相关。\n\n2. **广告服务 (adservice) 延迟显著升高**\n   - adservice 的 `rrt` 和 `rrt_max` 指标显著变坏，分别从 3053.55 上升到 20591.89，以及从 42999 上升到 192065。\n   - 运行于 `aiops-k8s-03` 上的其他 Pod 没有显著问题，可能提示 adservice 服务有特定问题亟待解决。\n\n3. **cartservice 的最大响应时间变化**\n   - `rrt_max` 指标显著变坏，可能与节点（aiops-k8s-08）或服务自身调用链有关。\n\n### JSON 输出\n```json\n{\n  \"stance\": \"NEUTRAL\",\n  \"detected_metric_keys\": [\"pod_cpu_usage\", \"rrt\", \"rrt_max\"],\n  \"hypotheses\": [\n    {\n      \"component\": \"aiops-k8s-08\",\n      \"reason\": \"Pod资源消耗增加导致服务水平下降，影响Pod adservice-1, adservice-2, adservice-0的CPU使用率变化（pod_cpu_usage）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"Pod的cpu使用率从0.0增长到0.6, 变化率达到2.0\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"adservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"adservice服务响应时间显著增加，可能与服务自身瓶颈或请求负载有关（rrt, rrt_max）\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt从3053.55升至20591.89，变化率为1.4834；rrt_max从42999升至192065，变化率为1.2683\"\n    },\n    {\n      \"component\": \"cartservice\",\n      \"reason\": \"cartservice最大响应时间显著变化（rrt_max），可能与服务负载或节点资源问题有关\",\n      \"evidence\": \"rrt_max从14561升至14874, 变化率为1.4718\"\n    }\n  ]\n}\n```\n\n请根据上述发现继续深入调查底层原因或关联分析。必要时，查看节点日志及服务详细调用链。"}
